for you, sir.

492
00:24:05,877 --> 00:24:07,377
Okay, hit me with it.

493
00:24:07,379 --> 00:24:08,912
Do you have any advice
on how to get adopted?

494
00:24:08,914 --> 00:24:10,046
Oh, yeah.
Oh, you do?

495
00:24:10,048 --> 00:24:11,080
