can I get an autograph?

496
00:24:11,082 --> 00:24:12,882
Sure.

497
00:24:12,884 --> 00:24:14,250
Um, all right, for example,
is teeth whitener a good idea?

498
00:24:14,252 --> 00:24:15,552
Yes.
There you go, pal.
Thanks!

499
00:24:15,554 --> 00:24:16,820
Really?
Oh, yeah.

500
00:24:16,822 --> 00:24:18,421
Looking good, Bruce.
Thank you so much.

501
00:24:18,423 --> 00:24:20,423
How about eyeliner
or a foreign language?

502
00:24:20,425 --> 00:24:21,958
Try both.
<i> Bueno.</i>

503
00:24:21,960 --> 00:24:23,726
Look, it's
the new commissioner!

504
00:24:23,728 --> 00:24:25,462
