in the market
to adopt a child?

514
00:24:55,660 --> 00:24:57,260
Yeah.
Really?

515
00:24:57,262 --> 00:24:58,995
Oh, yeah.
Wow.

516
00:24:58,997 --> 00:25:00,830
Are you looking for more
of a base model orphan

517
