upgraded features?
Yep.

518
00:25:03,268 --> 00:25:04,801
Like cooking
or driftwood art?

519
00:25:04,803 --> 00:25:06,202
Gymnastic abilities?
Yep. Yep.

520
00:25:06,204 --> 00:25:07,837
Close-up street magic
a la David Blaine?

521
00:25:07,839 --> 00:25:09,839
All of it
sounds great.
Really?

522
00:25:09,841 --> 00:25:13,376
Because all of it
sounds like me.

523
00:25:13,378 --> 00:25:16,379
Mr. Wayne, do you think you'd
be interested in adopting me

524
00:25:16,381 --> 00:25:18,181
