525
00:25:18,183 --> 00:25:19,315
Definitely.

526
00:25:19,317 --> 00:25:20,884
Oh, this is great!

527
00:25:20,886 --> 00:25:22,552
Because all I want
is to get adopted,

528
00:25:22,554 --> 00:25:24,220
so I can finally stop being

529
00:25:26,690 --> 00:25:29,325
alone.

530
00:25:29,327 --> 00:25:30,727
<i> We've gathered </i>
<i> here tonight</i>

