598
00:27:56,007 --> 00:27:58,107
She's making
a lot of sense.

599
00:27:58,109 --> 00:27:59,809
Excuse me.
I'm so sorry. Excuse me.

600
00:27:59,811 --> 00:28:01,511
We love you,
Barbara!

601
00:28:01,513 --> 00:28:03,446
Yes.
Hi. Bruce Wayne.

602
00:28:03,448 --> 00:28:05,515
Billionaire, bon vivant,
gallivanter, playboy,

603
00:28:05,517 --> 00:28:07,684
Gotham's most
eligible bachelor,

604
00:28:07,686 --> 00:28:08,818
like, 90 years in a row.

605
00:28:08,820 --> 00:28:10,119
That's me right there.

606
00:28:10,121 --> 00:28:11,187
<i> I know who you are,</i>
<i> Mr. Wayne.</i>

607
00:28:11,189 --> 00:28:12,789
You bet you do.
Quick quest,

608
00:28:12,791 --> 00:28:15,158
what is your problem
with Batman,

609
00:28:15,160 --> 00:28:17,660
and also,
what the heck, dude?

610
00:28:17,662 --> 00:28:19,295
<i> I'm glad you asked,</i>
<i> Mr. Wayne.</i>

611
00:28:19,297 --> 00:28:21,497
<i> I'm not a Batman hater.</i>

612
00:28:21,499 --> 00:28:24,067
