<i> and proper ethics</i>

616
00:28:34,646 --> 00:28:36,212
<i> and accountability.</i>

617
00:28:36,214 --> 00:28:37,647
I hate everything
you just said.

618
00:28:37,649 --> 00:28:40,850
<i> Because my dream</i>
<i> is for the police force</i>

619
00:28:40,852 --> 00:28:42,719
