620
00:28:42,721 --> 00:28:44,087
Waiter.

621
00:28:44,089 --> 00:28:45,722
<i> Wouldn't that be better?</i>

622
00:28:45,724 --> 00:28:47,557
<i> And I know that, together,</i>

623
00:28:47,559 --> 00:28:49,559
<i> the world's</i>
<i> greatest detective...</i>

624
00:28:49,561 --> 00:28:51,728
<i> ...and Gotham's finest</i>

625
00:28:51,730 --> 00:28:54,030
