629
00:29:03,742 --> 00:29:06,409
<i> Everyone! Make your way</i>
<i> to the exits immediately!</i>

630
00:29:06,411 --> 00:29:07,844
Run!

631
00:29:07,846 --> 00:29:09,879
Team bane,
block the exits.

632
00:29:09,881 --> 00:29:11,581
Going somewhere?

633
00:29:11,583 --> 00:29:14,250
Clayface, freeze, bring me
the new commissioner Gordon.

634
00:29:14,252 --> 00:29:16,052
We're on it.
Cool.

635
00:29:16,054 --> 00:29:18,020
And, Harley,
you know what to do.

636
00:29:18,022 --> 00:29:19,589
I sure do.

637
00:29:19,591 --> 00:29:22,925
It's time for operation
"take out the laundry."

638
00:29:22,927 --> 00:29:26,095
Butler one, this is
bat one. Do you copy?

639
00:29:26,097 --> 00:29:27,563
Go ahead, bat one.

640
00:29:27,565 --> 00:29:28,898
<i> I need my armored</i>
<i> face disguise, now!</i>

641
00:29:28,900 --> 00:29:30,399
Only if you say
the magic word.

642
00:29:30,401 --> 00:29:31,534
Now!
<i> No.</i>

643
00:29:31,536 --> 00:29:32,735
