646
00:29:37,908 --> 00:29:39,208
- Hey, 'puter.
<i>- Yes?</i>

647
00:29:39,210 --> 00:29:41,077
Initialize masterbuild music.

648
00:29:41,079 --> 00:29:42,912
<i> Right away.</i>

649
00:29:42,914 --> 00:29:46,115
<i> Collateral damage assessment</i>
<i> suggests the scuttler, sir.</i>

650
00:29:46,117 --> 00:29:47,283
Good plan.

651
00:29:52,089 --> 00:29:54,390
Madam mayor,
stay close to me.

652
00:29:54,392 --> 00:29:56,058
Head for the south exit.

653
00:29:56,060 --> 00:29:57,160
Now, ma'am.

654
00:29:59,063 --> 00:30:00,329
Go! Go! Go!

655
00:30:00,331 --> 00:30:01,764
Honey, let Batman
take care of it.

656
00:30:01,766 --> 00:30:03,299
Dad, I got this.

657
00:30:15,445 --> 00:30:17,113
<i> Scuttler online.</i>

658
00:30:17,115 --> 00:30:19,315
