660
00:30:25,455 --> 00:30:28,157
Chief,
get the mayor to safety.

661
00:30:28,159 --> 00:30:30,660
Computer, I've got
the joker in my sights.

662
00:30:30,662 --> 00:30:32,829
Team, I got the joker
in my sights.

663
00:30:37,334 --> 00:30:38,467
Joker!

664
00:30:38,469 --> 00:30:39,702
Joker.

665
00:30:39,704 --> 00:30:41,304
Uh, excuse me?
I was about to...

666
00:30:41,306 --> 00:30:43,005
Push the bat-signal?
Good call.

667
00:30:43,007 --> 00:30:44,440
I like your instincts.

668
00:30:44,442 --> 00:30:46,342
