And it's gonna
make you smile.

670
00:30:48,479 --> 00:30:50,613
Uh-oh!
His smile is our grimace.

671
00:30:50,615 --> 00:30:51,681
Everybody, get down.

672
00:30:51,683 --> 00:30:52,815
I...

673
