"i...Surrender."

678
00:31:03,962 --> 00:31:05,461
Joker,
what are you doing?

679
00:31:05,463 --> 00:31:07,363
I'm sorry, my bat-ears
must be malfunctioning

680
00:31:07,365 --> 00:31:08,497
because it sounds...

681
