There is no "us."

686
00:31:18,042 --> 00:31:21,544
So, there's no point in me
trying to fight you anymore.

687
00:31:21,546 --> 00:31:24,046
Therefore,
i will be surrendering myself

688
00:31:24,048 --> 00:31:26,883
