and forward-thinking
new commissioner.

689
00:31:26,885 --> 00:31:28,885
Blink, blink, blink.
Blinkety blink, blink, blink!

690
00:31:28,887 --> 00:31:30,253
That's really suspicious.

691
00:31:30,255 --> 00:31:32,221
Yeah, it is.
What are you up to, joker?

692
00:31:32,223 --> 00:31:34,857
I just wanna go to arkham
