saying "blink"?

695
00:31:38,830 --> 00:31:40,229
No! Blink, blink, blink.

696
00:31:40,231 --> 00:31:41,397
<i> Joker! That's enough.</i>

697
00:31:41,399 --> 00:31:43,165
Okay, babs. I got this.

698
00:31:43,167 --> 00:31:46,736
