713
00:32:14,299 --> 00:32:17,033
Because we're
all surrendering.

714
00:32:17,035 --> 00:32:18,200
Right, guys?

715
00:32:18,202 --> 00:32:19,268
We are?

716
00:32:19,270 --> 00:32:20,469
Yes!

717
00:32:28,212 --> 00:32:30,947
Riddle me this.
What just happened?

718
00:32:30,949 --> 00:32:32,615
It's the end of crime!

719
00:32:32,617 --> 00:32:34,050
All right!

720
00:32:34,052 --> 00:32:34,884
That was amazing!
Over here, over here!

721
00:32:34,886 --> 00:32:35,952
You did it!

722
00:32:35,954 --> 00:32:37,553
Yeah, of course
i did. I'm...

723
00:32:37,555 --> 00:32:38,754
Sorry, not you.

724
00:32:38,756 --> 00:32:40,489
We're talking
to commissioner Gordon.

725
00:32:40,491 --> 00:32:42,258
Well, it was
a team effort.
I got this, babs.

726
00:32:42,260 --> 00:32:43,793
