how do you feel?

727
00:32:43,795 --> 00:32:46,128
Amazing!
This is a great first day.

728
00:32:46,130 --> 00:32:47,463
Okay.

729
00:32:47,465 --> 00:32:49,098
Question for Batman.
Shoot.

730
00:32:49,100 --> 00:32:50,566
What are you gonna do
with the rest of your life?

