01:34:51,385 --> 01:34:54,053
Wait a minute,
we're not just gonna
let these criminals go, right?

2224
01:34:54,055 --> 01:34:55,688
Ah, come on, commish.
Let's face it.

2225
01:34:55,690 --> 01:34:57,856
Those guys are no match
for the four of us.

2226
01:34:57,858 --> 01:34:59,692
We'll give them
a 30-minute head start.

2227
01:34:59,694 --> 01:35:02,494
Besides, you can't fight crime
on an empty stomach.

2228
01:35:05,231 --> 01:35:06,632
Hey, computer?

2229
01:35:06,634 --> 01:35:07,966
We're home!

2230
01:35:11,504 --> 01:35:12,805
<i> What is the password?</i>

2231
01:35:12,807 --> 01:35:14,540
Iron man sucks!

2232
01:35:26,553 --> 01:35:27,753
When dad
and me were fighting,

2233
01:35:27,755 --> 01:35:29,488
I was giving them
my best one-liners.

2234
01:35:30,223 --> 01:35:31,290
<i> You</i>

2235
01:35:33,393 --> 01:35:35,094
<i> complete me.</i>

2236
01:35:48,341 --> 01:35:51,443
Holy family photo, Batman.
I love it!

2237
01:35:58,351 --> 01:35:59,752
<i> White.</i>

2238
01:35:59,754 --> 01:36:04,356
<i> All important movies end</i>
<i> with a white screen.</i>

2239
01:36:04,358 --> 01:36:06,592
<i> And tying up loose ends.</i>

2240
01:36:06,594 --> 01:36:08,861
We're coming for you,
Gotham city!

2241
01:36:08,863 --> 01:36:10,395
<i> Like </i>
<i> this snake clowns bit.</i>

2242
01:36:10,397 --> 01:36:11,630
<i> Snake clowns?</i>

2243
01:36:11,632 --> 01:36:13,298
<i> Told you </i>
<i> they were real.</i>

2244
01:36:13,300 --> 01:36:15,033
<i> Did you stick wigs </i>
<i> onto snakes?</i>

2245
01:36:15,035 --> 01:36:17,069
<i>- Maybe.</i>
<i>- That is so weird.</i>

2246
01:36:17,071 --> 01:36:18,637
<i> Can I play that song </i>
<i> I wrote for the end credits?</i>

2247
01:36:18,639 --> 01:36:19,905
<i> That is a hard pass.</i>

2248
01:36:19,907 --> 01:36:21,774
<i>- Come on.</i>
<i>- No!</i>

2249
01:36:21,776 --> 01:36:23,208
<i> Let the kid play </i>
<i> whatever music he wants.</i>

2250
01:36:23,210 --> 01:36:24,443
<i>- No, no, no!</i>
<i>- Please?</i>

2251
01:36:24,445 --> 01:36:25,611
<i>- No.</i>
- Padre?

2252
01:36:25,613 --> 01:36:27,379
<i> Fine. 'Puter.</i>

2253
01:36:27,381 --> 01:36:28,714
<i> Okay, sir.</i>

2254
01:36:28,716 --> 01:36:30,649
<i> Yay!</i>

2255
01:36:30,651 --> 01:36:32,618
<i> Now playing </i>
<i> Robin's happy, poppy music.</i>

2256
01:36:32,620 --> 01:36:35,954
<i> The kind that makes parents</i>
<i> and studio executives happy.</i>

2257
01:36:59,646 --> 01:37:00,712
Come on, everyone!

2258
01:37:20,266 --> 01:37:21,667
Come on, Batman!
No!

2259
01:38:48,888 --> 01:38:51,523
Wow, that was fun!

2260
01:38:51,525 --> 01:38:54,059
Really hope
nobody was recording that.

2261
01:38:54,061 --> 01:38:55,627
Let me see.
Oh, this thing is on.

2262
01:38:55,629 --> 01:38:56,628
This thing is recording.
